<div style="margin: 10px 0 0 10px;">
<h1 style="font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 0 10px 0;">Welcome to Brigham Young University-Idaho</h1>
<p style="margin: 0 10px 10px 0;">What began with a simple announcement in 2000 has now emerged as a first-class educational institution. At Brigham Young University-Idaho, students achieve superior academic abilities, learn to become dedicated disciples and leaders, and acquire practical experience that prepares them to successfully contribute wherever they live and serve. Take a moment and learn about all that BYU-Idaho has to offer.</p>
<div style="margin: 0 0 0 10px;">
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x9274.xml"><img alt="taylor building" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/BYUImission.jpg" width="78" /></a></div>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;">
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="x9274.xml">BYU-Idaho's Mission</a></h3>
<p>BYU-Idaho is continually working to develop "disciple-leaders." Read BYU-Idaho&rsquo;s Mission Statement and learn how the university prepares students for their future roles in the Church and in the world.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x9272.xml"><img alt="students in classroom" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/becomingBYUI.jpg" width="78" /></a></div>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;">
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="x9272.xml">Becoming BYU-Idaho</a></h3>
<p>BYU-Idaho is in the midst of a great season of innovation. Yet, at its core are values that have remained constant for over 100 years. Learn about the school's transition from Rick's College and the ingenuity that propels BYU-Idaho forward on its steady upward course.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x9273.xml"><img alt="Learning Model" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/bystudyandbyfaith.jpg" width="78" /></a></div>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;">
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="x9273.xml">By Study and by Faith</a></h3>
<p>BYU-Idaho is a teaching-focused, student-centered university. With the help of inspired and dedicated faculty members, coupled with a unique learning model that provides a deeper academic experience, students gain greater knowledge through study and faith.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x9249.xml"><img alt="Student Activities" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/beaparticipant.jpg" width="78" /></a></div>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;">
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="x9249.xml">Be a Participant</a></h3>
<p>The Student Activities Program offers something for everyone. From rock climbing to humanitarian service, participants gain valuable experience and develop personal and spiritual qualities that prepare them for life&mdash;a perfect complement to their scholastic opportunities.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x9275.xml"><img alt="campus life" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/campuslife.jpg" width="78" /> </a></div>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;">
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="x9275.xml">Campus Life</a></h3>
<p>In addition to powerful academic offerings, students at BYU-Idaho benefit from a robust university experience that includes secular learning, spiritual preparation, social and physical activities, and opportunities to build lifelong relationships.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x9276.xml"><img alt="graduate" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/graduates.jpg" width="78" /> </a></div>
<a href="http://beta.byui.edu/About_BYUI/About_BYU-Idaho/Graduates.html"> </a>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;"><a href="http://beta.byui.edu/About_BYUI/About_BYU-Idaho/Graduates.html"> </a>
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="x9276.xml">Graduates</a></h3>
<p>BYU-Idaho graduates are making a significant difference as they leave campus and move across the world&mdash;providing examples of faith, humility, gratitude, hard work, and service to all they come in contact with.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="gray-box" style="background-color: #efefec; margin: 0 0 10px 0; display: block; width: 100%; height: 104px;">
<div class="image" style="float: left; margin: 0 10px 0 0; display: block; width: 90px;"><a href="x11128.xml"><img alt="Ricks Academy" height="104" src="Images/Admin_Offices/university_communications/About_byui/ourlegacy.jpg" width="78" /> </a></div>
<a href="http://beta.byui.edu/About_BYUI/About_BYU-Idaho/Our_Legacy.html"> </a>
<div class="text" style="float: left; display: block; width: 530px;"><a href="http://beta.byui.edu/About_BYUI/About_BYU-Idaho/Our_Legacy.html"> </a>
<h3 style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;"><a href="http://beta.byui.edu/About_BYUI/About_BYU-Idaho/Our_Legacy.html"></a><a href="x11128.xml">Our Legacy</a></h3>
<p>For more than a hundred years, BYU-Idaho has enjoyed a lasting legacy of sacrifice, service, and faith that continues on campus today. Discover the rich heritage of BYU-Idaho and share in the legacy.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
